Package org.jamsim.ascape

Ascape specific classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ScapeData
    Defines data external to a scape that can be accessed by agents.
    ScapeDataCreator<D extends ScapeData>
    Factory method interface for creating a ScapeData object.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConsoleOutput
    Adapt the Ascape ConsoleOutView to the Output interface.
    DataDictionary
    Dictionary mapping variable names to their description.
    MicroSimCell<D extends ScapeData>
    MicroSimCell is a Cell that provides functionality for getting/setting ScapeData and weights.
    MicroSimScape<D extends ScapeData>
    A Scape with micro-simulation input/output functions including base file loading, and output tables and external / global data tables that appear in the Ascape Navigator.
    MultipleRunController
    Automatically rerun the simulation a specified number of times.
    RootScape<D extends ScapeData>
    Root scape that initialises and loads agents into a base microsimulation scape.
    RunAscape
    Start Ascape with the supplied scape.

Package org.jamsim.ascape Description

Ascape specific classes. Have dependencies with Ascape.
